        h2: 'Offer Design Consultations and Financing Options Online',
        body: `High-ticket furniture purchases are often emotionally complex. Customers worry about getting the wrong size, the wrong style, or making a decision their partner doesn\'t agree with. Offering a free online design consultation — bookable through your website — gives them the expert guidance they need to feel confident, and gives your sales team the opportunity to build rapport and close a higher-value sale.\n\nPublicly offering financing options on your website is equally important. Many customers who want your $2,000 sofa will buy a $500 alternative from a competitor simply because they didn\'t know financing was available. Featuring financing prominently on product pages and the homepage removes that barrier and opens the sale to a wider audience.`
