        h2: 'Building a referral engine from past customers',
        body: `A happy roofing customer knows ten homeowners in their neighborhood who have the same roof age. A referral ask — automated via email 60 days after project completion — paired with a small incentive (a gift card, a free gutter inspection) generates word-of-mouth leads at a fraction of the cost of paid advertising.\n\nTracking referral sources in your CRM lets you identify which customers send the most business and double down on those relationships. Some roofing companies generate 40–50% of their annual revenue from a referral program alone.`,
